topic.title: Now Available: Nineteen Newly Digitized Foreign Relations Volumes
topic.body: This release is part of the Office’s ongoing project, in partnership with the University of Wisconsin Digital Collections Center, to digitize the entire Foreign Relations series. These volumes cover events that took place between 1943 and 1948 and were originally published in print between 1957 and 1973.
